  "general_provisions": "This bill amends provisions related to motor vehicle title brands.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>defines terms, including terms for motor vehicle title brands;<hr><ltbullet>describes the circumstances under which a salvaged vehicle may receive a brand of rebuilt and restored;<hr><ltbullet>requires the Motor Vehicle Division to check a national database before issuing a new Utah title; and<hr><ltbullet>makes technical changes.",
